::DrillBit::

"Your looking for Deemos? Him and his group attacked this base three
times, in the last two days. All the damage you see is his fault. And we
lost two Predicons, to them." He said, to the new bot. DrillBit observed
KitKat and Phobia. He knew that KitKat needed her space, especially now
that she was second in command, but something made him want to see what
they were talking about. He walked up, to them.
"Whats going on?" He asked.
